node.text: In response to the COVID-19 pandemic, @voguemagazine and @cfda have launched A Common Thread, an initiative to support independent fashion designers whose businesses have been impacted by the pandemic, including the pattern makers, cutters, tailors, embroiderers, and so many more business and creative employees. Visit amazon.com/commonthreads to learn more about how you can help, or donate through Alexa by saying, “Alexa, donate to A Common Thread.” From all of us at @amazonfashion, @voguemagazine, and the @cfda, we thank you for your support. 🖤 #founditonamazon

node.title: Discover new independent designers & support the American fashion industry
